      <title>意大利将提高比特币资本利得税</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2024-10-16/italy-to-raise-capital-gains-tax-on-bitcoin</link>
      <description><![CDATA[意大利计划将比特币的资本利得税从 26% 提高到 42%，这是为削减财政赤字的同时兑现昂贵的竞选承诺而做出的努力的一部分。Sonali Basak 报道了这一消息。（来源：彭博社）]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2024-10-16/italy-to-raise-capital-gains-tax-on-bitcoin</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 16 Oct 2024 20:33:36 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>Ripple 总裁 Gary Gensler 谈加密货币“战争之路”</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2024-10-16/gary-gensler-on-crypto-warpath-ripple-president</link>
      <description><![CDATA[Ripple 总裁 Monica Long 讨论了加密货币的不确定性，并表示美国证券交易委员会的 Gary Gensler 多年来一直在“战斗”。她在“Bloomberg Crypto”节目中与 Sonali Basak 和 Tim Stenovec 进行了交谈。（来源：彭博社）]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2024-10-16/gary-gensler-on-crypto-warpath-ripple-president</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 16 Oct 2024 20:26:42 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>Crucible Capital 的批评者称，加密货币市场“上涨”</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2024-10-16/it-is-uptober-for-crypto-says-crucible-capital-s-demirors</link>
      <description><![CDATA[Crucible Capital 普通合伙人 Meltem Demirors 表示，随着比特币价格接近 70,000 美元，现在是“上涨”的时候了。她在“Bloomberg Crypto”节目中与 Sonali Basak 和 Tim Stenovec 进行了交谈。（来源：彭博社）]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2024-10-16/it-is-uptober-for-crypto-says-crucible-capital-s-demirors</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 16 Oct 2024 20:26:01 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>Demirors：无论谁担任总统，加密货币都是不可阻挡的</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2024-10-16/crypto-is-unstoppable-whoever-is-president-demirors-video</link>
      <description><![CDATA[Crucible Capital 普通合伙人 Meltem Demirors 表示“谁当总统其实并不重要”，加密货币是一股“不可阻挡的力量”。她在“彭博加密货币”节目中与 Tim Stenovec 进行了交谈。
（来源：彭博社）]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2024-10-16/crypto-is-unstoppable-whoever-is-president-demirors-video</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 16 Oct 2024 20:05:44 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>长期国债的公允价值：Nuveen 的 Rodriguez</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2024-10-16/long-end-of-treasuries-at-fair-value-nuveen-s-rodriguez-video</link>
      <description><![CDATA[Nuveen 固定收益策略主管 Tony Rodriguez 表示，他预计美联储将缓慢而有条不紊地降息，高利率可能会持续一段时间。在接受“Bloomberg The Close”采访时，Rodriguez 还讨论了他在当前利率环境下的固定收益投资策略。（来源：彭博社）]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2024-10-16/long-end-of-treasuries-at-fair-value-nuveen-s-rodriguez-video</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 16 Oct 2024 20:04:39 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>RNA 编辑股票因 Wave Life 的试验数据而创纪录飙升</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-16/rna-editing-stocks-soar-on-wave-life-s-breakthrough-trial-data</link>
      <description><![CDATA[周三，一项临床试验的突破性数据显示了 RNA 编辑疗法的治疗前景，研发该疗法的公司股价随之上涨。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-16/rna-editing-stocks-soar-on-wave-life-s-breakthrough-trial-data</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 16 Oct 2024 16:57:33 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>调查受挫后，Ecopetrol 发行 17.5 亿美元债券</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-16/ecopetrol-ec-restarts-dollar-debt-deal-after-ceo-probe-drove-delay</link>
      <description><![CDATA[Ecopetrol SA 再次试水海外市场，发行了价值 17.5 亿美元的债券。一周前，该公司因涉及首席执行官的调查而推迟了交易。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-16/ecopetrol-ec-restarts-dollar-debt-deal-after-ceo-probe-drove-delay</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 16 Oct 2024 14:45:52 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
