      <title>Novavax 因安全性问题暂停流感和新冠疫苗研究</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-16/novavax-shares-plunge-after-fda-places-a-hold-on-its-flu-shots</link>
      <description><![CDATA[由于一名研究志愿者出现严重的神经疾病，美国监管机构暂停了 Novavax Inc. 的实验疫苗研发，随后该公司股价下跌 19%。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-16/novavax-shares-plunge-after-fda-places-a-hold-on-its-flu-shots</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 16 Oct 2024 13:39:12 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>230 亿美元养老金投票给乌拉圭大选蒙上阴影</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-16/a-23-billion-pension-vote-is-overshadowing-uruguay-s-election</link>
      <description><![CDATA[作为拉丁美洲富人的天堂，乌拉圭人即将决定是否要改革其社会保障体系。这项耗资 230 亿美元的提案备受争议，给即将到来的总统大选蒙上了阴影。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-16/a-23-billion-pension-vote-is-overshadowing-uruguay-s-election</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 16 Oct 2024 12:00:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
